<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>For My Love ❤️</title>

<style>
*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
}

body{
    font-family:'Segoe UI',sans-serif;
    min-height:100vh;
    background:linear-gradient(-45deg,#ff4d6d,#ff758f,#ff8fa3,#ffc2d1);
    background-size:400% 400%;
    animation:bg 12s ease infinite;
    overflow:hidden;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:center;
}

@keyframes bg{
    0%{background-position:0% 50%;}
    50%{background-position:100% 50%;}
    100%{background-position:0% 50%;}
}

.card{
    width:90%;
    max-width:850px;
    background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    backdrop-filter:blur(12px);
    border-radius:30px;
    padding:40px;
    text-align:center;
    color:white;
    box-shadow:0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.2);
    z-index:10;
}

h1{
    font-size:3rem;
    margin-bottom:15px;
}

.subtitle{
    font-size:1.2rem;
    opacity:.9;
    margin-bottom:25px;
}

.message{
    line-height:1.9;
    font-size:1.2rem;
}

button{
    margin-top:25px;
    border:none;
    padding:15px 30px;
    border-radius:50px;
    cursor:pointer;
    font-size:1rem;
    background:white;
    color:#ff4d6d;
    font-weight:bold;
    transition:.3s;
}

button:hover{
    transform:scale(1.08);
}

.hidden{
    display:none;
    margin-top:25px;
    font-size:1.15rem;
    line-height:1.8;
}

.heart{
    position:absolute;
    color:white;
    animation:float linear infinite;
    opacity:.8;
}

@keyframes float{
    from{ziad
        transform:translateY(100vh);
    }
    to{loki❣️
        transform:translateY(-120px);
    }
}

.star{
    position:absolute;
    color:white;
    animation:twinkle 2s infinite;
}

@keyframes twinkle{
    0%,100%{opacity:.2;}
    50%{opacity:1;}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="card">

<h1>❤️ For [loki] ❤️</h1>

<p class="subtitle">
The most beautiful girl in my world
</p>

<div class="message">
You are the most beautiful person I have ever known.

Every time I think about you, my heart feels full.
Your smile lights up my darkest days, and your presence
makes everything feel better.

I love you more than words can explain.
I don't want to leave you.
I don't want to lose you.

I am holding on because you mean so much to me.
You are special, precious, and truly unforgettable.
</div>

<button onclick="showLove()">
❤️ Open My Heart ❤️
</button>

<div id="extra" class="hidden">
I promise to stand beside you, step by step.

When you feel strong, I will cheer for you.
When you feel tired, I will support you.
When you doubt yourself, I will remind you how amazing you are.

No matter where life takes us,
I will always care about you,
believe in you,
and encourage you to chase your dreams.

You are beautiful,
inside and out.

And if I could choose a thousand times,
I would still choose you. ❤️
</div>

</div>

<script>
function showLove(){
document.getElementById("extra").style.display="block";
}

for(let i=0;i<60;i++){
let heart=document.createElement("div");
heart.className="heart";
heart.innerHTML="❤️";
heart.style.left=Math.random()*100+"vw";
heart.style.fontSize=(15+Math.random()*25)+"px";
heart.style.animationDuration=(5+Math.random()*8)+"s";
document.body.appendChild(heart);
}

for(let i=0;i<70;i++){
let star=document.createElement("div");
star.className="star";
star.innerHTML="✨";
star.style.left=Math.random()*100+"vw";
star.style.top=Math.random()*100+"vh";
star.style.animationDelay=Math.random()*2+"s";
document.body.appendChild(star);
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
<h2 style="margin-top:30px;">
✨ Made With Love For Loki ✨
</h2>
